<br />
<br />After posting I went and gave the ravishings another go. Last time I tried to use one I think was 43 or 44. At 47 they were much easier to control. I was also able to kill roughly 2 or 3 times as many mobs before I had to burn down the pet. I got about 45% in a tad over an hour using 2 ragers and 2 ravishings.
<br />
